name: Google Ad Banner Template
description:
Google Ads - Banners - This library contains all sizes for your google advertising company..


Sizes support:

  • 250x250;
  • 200x200;
  • 300x250;
  • 336x280;
  • 970x250;
  • 970x90;
  • 728x90;
  • 468x60;
  • 320x100;
  • 120x600;
  • 160x600;
  • 300x600;
  • 240x400


How do I use this library?

  1. Copy the project from community to your profile in Figma
  2. Go to the copied project
  3. Remove or reuse context in all frames. Done!
